GDG DevFest Hanoi 2019 - The biggest event this year!

DevFest is a festival for developers community may cover multiple products such as Android, Firebase, Google Cloud Platform, Google Assistant, Flutter, machine learning with TensorFlow, and mobile web. This is one of the major annual events hosted by Google Developer Group in over 600 chapters in different countries around the world.

Events may include speaker sessions, hackathons, codelabs, study jams, and trainings with speakers from Google, Google Developers Experts, Women Techmaker Ambassadors and speakers from other companies.

The event is an opportunity for developers, young people who are passionate about technology, to get connected, interact and learn about each other, as well as to experience and update new technology trends around the world.

Link event: https://www.facebook.com/events/701545106997608/
Register here: http://bit.ly/GDGDevFestHanoi2019

events.name: Serverless and Machine Learning with Google Cloud
events.description:
Welcome to the first GDG Cloud Hanoi meetup for the year 2020!

For the first event, we would like to bring the following set of talks coming up:

✔ Topic 1: Serverless and Machine Learning with Google Cloud

Speaker: Grant Timmerman - Developer Platform Engineer @ Google
“Grant is a developer platform engineer at Google where he works on Google Cloud Platform. Previously he led open source for G Suite APIs. He loves Node, GitHub, and plays the alto saxophone in his spare time.”

📝 Synopsis:
Google Cloud Functions makes it easy for developers to run and scale code in the cloud and build event-driven serverless applications. Cloud AutoML helps you easily build high quality custom machine learning models with limited machine learning expertise needed. In this session you’ll learn how to combine these technologies to build impressive machine learning applications.
-----

✔ Topic 2: VM on Google Cloud and How to get Google Cloud certificate within 3 months

Speaker: Dang Duc Huy - Co-organizer of GDG Cloud Hanoi
“Huy is a DevOps Engineer at Gimasys. He has 3 years of experience in system administration. He is proficient in working with the Oracle database and Google Cloud Platform. With this expertise, he has received a Google Professional Cloud Architect certificate.”

Organizers: GDG Cloud Hanoi x Cloudfun (https://cloudfun.vn/)

⏰ 18:30 - 20:00 Tuesday, 21st Jan 2020
